WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.984
=Episode 31=

01:47.162 --> 01:47.563
You said

01:47.563 --> 01:48.643
to get me clothes.

01:59.003 --> 01:59.643
Haochen.

02:01.178 --> 02:04.763
â™ªI go surfing, go diving, go driving,
and go flying to a different placeâ™ª

02:04.763 --> 02:05.483
Haochen.

02:06.923 --> 02:08.403
Did you talk to me just now?

02:09.922 --> 02:10.722
I didn't hear it.

02:10.722 --> 02:11.642
Could you repeat that?

02:11.642 --> 02:12.403
Sorry.

02:13.722 --> 02:14.363
Haochen.

02:15.482 --> 02:16.363
Say it again, please.

02:17.482 --> 02:18.243
Haoming.

02:18.243 --> 02:20.162
What are you mumbling?

02:20.762 --> 02:21.243
Grandma.

02:22.003 --> 02:22.762
Did you hear that?

02:23.202 --> 02:24.683
Haochen spoke to me!

02:24.803 --> 02:25.803
I heard it.

02:25.843 --> 02:27.123
My ears work fine.

02:27.882 --> 02:29.202
Why are you so excited?

02:29.563 --> 02:30.202
Thank you.

02:30.243 --> 02:31.003
Don't mention it.

02:31.283 --> 02:33.602
He is very smart.

02:33.642 --> 02:34.602
He knows exactly

02:34.642 --> 02:36.083
who treats him well.

02:36.123 --> 02:38.123
This is his first step forward.

02:39.123 --> 02:40.083
Thank you, Grandma.

02:40.762 --> 02:42.123
For what?

02:42.482 --> 02:44.963
Your care is all that matters.

02:45.762 --> 02:46.602
Thank you.

02:48.363 --> 02:49.083
Haochen.

02:49.482 --> 02:50.283
Temperature's okay?

02:50.283 --> 02:51.683
I'll adjust it for you, okay?

02:52.240 --> 02:53.363
Need me to scrub your back?

02:54.003 --> 02:55.123
Tell me if you need help.

02:55.442 --> 02:56.563
I'll stay right here.

02:57.162 --> 02:58.042
I won't move at all.

02:58.642 --> 02:59.403
Right here.

03:02.083 --> 03:02.762
Haochen.

03:08.123 --> 03:08.963
It's ready.

03:09.963 --> 03:10.442
Here.

03:12.123 --> 03:13.162
Is it chilled?

03:14.003 --> 03:15.803
Of course. It's very sweet.

03:15.882 --> 03:16.523
Try it.

03:27.042 --> 03:28.083
How's Dad been lately?

03:30.083 --> 03:30.922
Mom said

03:31.403 --> 03:32.283
he is doing fine.

03:34.762 --> 03:35.363
Good then.

03:37.042 --> 03:38.202
Did you tell Mom

03:38.202 --> 03:38.922
the good news

03:39.083 --> 03:40.083
that Haochen talks now?

03:41.042 --> 03:41.602
Yes.

03:42.403 --> 03:43.363
She's thrilled.

03:45.482 --> 03:46.482
I really hope Haochen

03:46.482 --> 03:48.123
can recover sooner to his former

03:48.243 --> 03:49.403
lively and playful self.

03:50.442 --> 03:51.003
He will.

03:52.042 --> 03:53.563
Just give him more time.

03:55.482 --> 03:57.123
I've told Dr. Wang about

03:57.202 --> 03:58.442
Haochen's recent progress.

04:00.283 --> 04:01.523
Dr. Wang said it's excellent.

04:02.843 --> 04:03.722
This shows

04:04.403 --> 04:06.003
Grandma's methods really work.

04:06.882 --> 04:07.363
Right?

04:11.322 --> 04:12.602
Actually, I've always thought

04:13.322 --> 04:14.162
Grandma is

04:14.162 --> 04:15.563
an exceptionally wise person.

04:16.723 --> 04:17.642
She's attentive

04:18.683 --> 04:20.123
and great at caring for children,

04:20.442 --> 04:21.163
even

04:21.163 --> 04:22.163
playing along with them.

04:24.082 --> 04:24.522
Wherever

04:24.522 --> 04:25.762
Grandma is present,

04:26.803 --> 04:28.123
I feel completely at ease.

04:30.882 --> 04:31.842
Grandma is

04:31.842 --> 04:33.322
your steadfast anchor.

04:34.563 --> 04:35.603
And you are

04:35.603 --> 04:37.082
my steadfast anchor.

04:41.882 --> 04:43.003
Why suddenly say

04:43.003 --> 04:44.003
such cheesy things?

04:45.563 --> 04:47.043
I saw your photo album

04:47.642 --> 04:48.683
in your room today.

04:50.123 --> 04:51.243
Or rather,

04:51.363 --> 04:52.522
our photo album.

04:56.043 --> 04:57.842
How did you find that?

05:02.483 --> 05:03.842
The album

05:04.322 --> 05:06.603
ends when we were splitting up.

05:08.563 --> 05:09.642
I'm so glad

05:10.363 --> 05:12.123
we can take more photos together.

05:31.803 --> 05:32.882
Why take photos now?

05:34.923 --> 05:36.442
I want to add this photo

05:37.003 --> 05:37.882
to the album

05:38.923 --> 05:40.442
as our new page.

05:41.043 --> 05:42.363
Then I'll write

05:42.402 --> 05:44.923
"Today's watermelon was sweet."

05:58.762 --> 06:00.282
We have to keep recording.

06:01.082 --> 06:02.642
Even when we grow old,

06:03.082 --> 06:04.202
we will

06:05.363 --> 06:06.483
admire the moon here

06:06.962 --> 06:08.442
with endless things to talk about.

06:10.882 --> 06:12.123
Now I finally understand

06:12.123 --> 06:13.842
what mutual devotion really means.

06:14.563 --> 06:15.322
Do you know?

06:16.483 --> 06:17.282
It's like

06:18.282 --> 06:19.123
you imagine,

06:19.282 --> 06:20.043
and I do along.

06:24.962 --> 06:26.003
Want more watermelon?

06:26.322 --> 06:26.803
Okay.

06:32.123 --> 06:33.563
The moon is bright tonight.

06:36.563 --> 06:37.043
Look.

06:46.842 --> 06:47.483
Look.

06:56.563 --> 06:58.243
You've all heard the news, right?

06:59.043 --> 07:00.043
In real estate circles,

07:01.282 --> 07:03.043
there's been
a major development recently.

07:05.003 --> 07:07.043
The North Waichuan area in East China.

07:07.642 --> 07:08.603
You're interested in it?

07:09.123 --> 07:10.003
This will be

07:10.603 --> 07:11.603
my first major project

07:11.603 --> 07:12.642
since taking over Jinda.

07:13.762 --> 07:14.603
Only obtaining

07:14.603 --> 07:16.043
such achievements

07:17.483 --> 07:20.003
will silence the skeptics.

07:20.202 --> 07:20.803
Mr. Qu.

07:21.243 --> 07:22.522
I'll support you

07:22.762 --> 07:23.522
and give it my all.

07:25.603 --> 07:26.402
Weiping.

07:27.642 --> 07:28.882
How are Shen Haoming

07:29.402 --> 07:30.563
and Shen Jinsong?

07:31.402 --> 07:32.082
Godfather.

07:32.723 --> 07:33.762
Shen Haoming

07:33.762 --> 07:34.842
has left Jingzhou

07:34.842 --> 07:35.842
with Xu Yan and the child

07:36.282 --> 07:37.683
to lie low somewhere.

07:38.363 --> 07:39.603
And Shen Jinsong remains

07:39.603 --> 07:40.762
in a coma.

07:45.123 --> 07:45.723
Mr. Qu.

07:46.923 --> 07:48.683
Do you think

07:49.003 --> 07:50.320
Shen Haoming

07:50.320 --> 07:51.152
can make a comeback?

07:53.003 --> 07:54.522
I believe he

07:54.563 --> 07:55.483
would never abandon

07:55.483 --> 07:56.842
this Diamond Plot.

07:59.522 --> 08:00.483
Monitor closely

08:01.123 --> 08:02.442
who he associates with.

08:16.723 --> 08:17.322
Tired?

08:18.522 --> 08:19.363
Want some water?

08:21.842 --> 08:22.803
This won't work.

08:23.363 --> 08:24.082
Use mine.

08:36.003 --> 08:36.682
Haochen.

08:37.363 --> 08:38.723
Grandma's cooking is delicious.

08:38.723 --> 08:39.483
Lunch is ready.

08:41.083 --> 08:41.682
Alright.

08:47.562 --> 08:48.162
Ignore me.

08:52.003 --> 08:52.922
Take a break.

08:58.363 --> 08:59.682
You've prepared the soil so well.

09:00.723 --> 09:01.762
The seeds in this patch

09:01.762 --> 09:03.603
will surely thrive better than others.

09:11.282 --> 09:12.323
He talks to you.

09:13.443 --> 09:14.443
Yet you still ignore him?

09:16.003 --> 09:17.243
Not even saving face for him?

09:18.843 --> 09:20.443
Dad isn't my real dad.

09:20.922 --> 09:22.243
Mom isn't my real mom.

09:23.003 --> 09:24.363
Brother isn't my real brother.

09:25.483 --> 09:26.963
I'm not even my true self.

09:29.162 --> 09:30.603
I don't know what to say.

09:34.323 --> 09:35.762
I just don't understand

09:36.562 --> 09:38.363
why he had to deceive me.

09:40.203 --> 09:41.882
Why didn't he acknowledge me?

09:44.762 --> 09:45.522
Haochen.

09:45.922 --> 09:47.123
Have you considered

09:48.882 --> 09:50.243
that back then, Shen Haoming

09:50.243 --> 09:51.562
was just a kid himself?

09:53.203 --> 09:54.003
When he accidentally

09:54.003 --> 09:54.963
learned he had a son,

09:55.323 --> 09:56.443
he was scared too.

09:56.802 --> 09:58.162
But he never considered

09:58.162 --> 09:58.963
abandoning you.

10:00.522 --> 10:01.642
He wanted to protect you.

10:06.562 --> 10:07.162
Of course,

10:08.203 --> 10:09.282
Haoming's dad

10:10.402 --> 10:12.282
also wanted to protect his son,

10:12.642 --> 10:14.443
so used a wrong way.

10:16.162 --> 10:17.522
However, their purposes

10:17.922 --> 10:19.243
were to protect you.

10:20.603 --> 10:22.083
Do you understand me?

10:27.162 --> 10:28.843
But he's deceived me.

10:29.562 --> 10:30.203
Exactly.

10:30.682 --> 10:32.203
He's deceived you.

10:32.682 --> 10:33.882
And it is wrong.

10:34.843 --> 10:35.682
Lies

10:35.723 --> 10:37.162
will eventually come to light.

10:37.562 --> 10:38.162
Everyone

10:38.162 --> 10:39.522
will pay the price for this.

10:41.762 --> 10:43.042
They're upset too.

10:47.042 --> 10:48.843
Whoever you are,

10:48.843 --> 10:49.963
in this family,

10:51.083 --> 10:52.642
they'd always love you deeply,

10:53.603 --> 10:54.963
and their love will never change.

10:57.282 --> 10:59.083
I know you can feel it,

10:59.562 --> 11:00.203
right?

11:04.323 --> 11:05.443
So I have to

11:05.443 --> 11:06.483
forgive them?

11:06.682 --> 11:07.522
Of course not.

11:09.042 --> 11:10.562
You can have your own decision.

11:11.522 --> 11:13.123
It's all up to you.

11:13.402 --> 11:14.802
You can do whatever you want.

11:17.483 --> 11:19.083
I just want to remind you

11:20.603 --> 11:21.922
that we all love you very much.

11:24.843 --> 11:26.123
This will never change.

11:27.282 --> 11:28.522
I believe you can understand.

11:31.802 --> 11:32.243
Really.

11:32.243 --> 11:33.603
Grandma's cooking is delicious.

11:33.882 --> 11:34.603
Potato!

11:37.323 --> 11:37.802
Let's go

11:38.203 --> 11:39.003
to have lunch.

11:40.483 --> 11:41.003
Let's go.

11:45.083 --> 11:45.963
Look at the potato.

11:47.922 --> 11:49.282
Freshly dug from the ground.

12:44.522 --> 12:45.083
Hello.

12:45.363 --> 12:46.843
Where's the convenience store?

12:47.042 --> 12:47.682
What?

12:48.083 --> 12:48.922
It's not close.

12:49.243 --> 12:50.323
Keep walking along

12:50.323 --> 12:51.203
this road.

12:51.402 --> 12:52.882
Then you'll reach a fork.

12:52.922 --> 12:53.723
Turn left there.

12:53.762 --> 12:54.483
Walk along.

12:54.483 --> 12:55.642
Turn right at the next fork.

12:55.843 --> 12:57.363
Walk about 500 meters more,

12:57.522 --> 12:58.802
you'll see that.

12:59.922 --> 13:01.483
Turn left first, then right.

13:01.522 --> 13:02.083
Exactly.

13:02.083 --> 13:02.682
Thank you.

13:02.963 --> 13:03.483
No problem.

13:12.882 --> 13:13.402
Haochen.

13:36.730 --> 13:38.619
(Hongxin Zhenyuan
Supermarket and Restaurant)

13:56.882 --> 13:57.483
Haochen!

14:00.083 --> 14:00.802
Haochen!

14:04.682 --> 14:05.243
Haochen!

14:18.562 --> 14:19.123
Haochen!

14:20.042 --> 14:20.802
I'm here.

14:24.042 --> 14:24.723
At midnight,

14:25.282 --> 14:26.003
why did you

14:26.003 --> 14:26.843
come out

14:28.843 --> 14:29.723
without telling me?

14:31.483 --> 14:32.723
I was so worried about you.

14:35.843 --> 14:36.723
Are you hurt?

14:41.483 --> 14:42.042
Hungry?

14:43.882 --> 14:44.802
Tell me then.

14:45.682 --> 14:46.522
I'll cook for you.

14:48.682 --> 14:49.203
Are you cold?

14:50.363 --> 14:51.363
You're sweating.

14:51.963 --> 14:52.922
Might catch a cold.

14:53.922 --> 14:54.723
Don't get chilled.

15:49.603 --> 15:50.363
Enough hangers?

15:51.162 --> 15:51.682
Yes.

15:53.843 --> 15:54.363
Grandma.

15:56.042 --> 15:57.642
Haoming and I decided

15:58.003 --> 15:59.522
to return to Jingzhou tomorrow.

16:00.963 --> 16:02.162
So soon?

16:04.882 --> 16:06.843
Haochen is getting better,

16:08.282 --> 16:09.282
but Haoming's dad

16:09.282 --> 16:10.123
is hospitalized.

16:11.042 --> 16:12.323
So we thought

16:12.963 --> 16:14.003
to get back soon.

16:16.443 --> 16:17.522
Hasn't he awoken yet?

16:19.483 --> 16:20.282
Not yet.

16:21.603 --> 16:23.802
Although his vitals are stable,

16:24.363 --> 16:25.723
he just hasn't awoken.

16:29.042 --> 16:30.162
Go back then.

16:30.802 --> 16:31.843
When people are ill,

16:32.162 --> 16:33.243
they need family

16:33.243 --> 16:34.443
the most.

16:36.123 --> 16:36.963
Tomorrow morning,

16:37.003 --> 16:38.083
I'll pack your luggage.

16:52.522 --> 16:54.282
I've told you many times

16:55.243 --> 16:56.203
to bring you to Jingzhou

16:56.203 --> 16:57.522
to take good care

16:57.682 --> 16:58.642
of you.

17:01.243 --> 17:02.162
Now,

17:03.203 --> 17:04.282
when trouble comes,

17:05.243 --> 17:06.762
we still need your care.

17:08.082 --> 17:09.562
Don't you remember?

17:10.082 --> 17:12.522
I'm your safe harbor.

17:13.443 --> 17:14.243
Yan.

17:15.042 --> 17:15.842
No matter

17:16.243 --> 17:18.163
what trouble or worries

17:18.163 --> 17:19.243
you have,

17:19.562 --> 17:21.562
you can always come home to me.

17:22.842 --> 17:24.522
I'll always be here for you.

17:33.203 --> 17:34.723
When we settle everything,

17:35.042 --> 17:37.042
I'll bring Haochen to visit again.

17:37.322 --> 17:39.362
That would make me so happy.

17:47.203 --> 17:47.683
Okay.

17:48.723 --> 17:49.203
Come on.

17:49.443 --> 17:49.883
Here.

17:52.762 --> 17:54.003
- I'll do it.
- It's soaked.

17:54.003 --> 17:54.723
Wring it dry.

17:55.243 --> 17:56.082
Take it.

17:56.322 --> 17:57.163
Yes, like that.

17:57.403 --> 17:58.443
Use both hands.

17:59.362 --> 18:00.003
Oh my!

18:00.243 --> 18:00.522
Come.

18:00.602 --> 18:01.203
Yes, yes.

18:02.003 --> 18:02.842
Okay. Wring it dry.

18:08.986 --> 18:10.842
(Yan Studio)

18:10.842 --> 18:11.963
Welcome back, Ms. Xu.

18:11.963 --> 18:13.403
Yan, I miss you so much.

18:13.403 --> 18:14.163
That's enough.

18:14.163 --> 18:15.082
Have a seat.

18:15.723 --> 18:16.322
Sit, sit.

18:17.562 --> 18:18.163
Recently,

18:18.163 --> 18:20.602
due to my personal matters,

18:21.282 --> 18:22.562
I've delayed the progress.

18:23.122 --> 18:24.163
But thanks to Lin

18:24.483 --> 18:25.522
and your efforts,

18:25.762 --> 18:27.483
Yan Studio is now operating smoothly.

18:29.322 --> 18:30.443
I especially want to thank

18:30.483 --> 18:32.122
our CFO Lin Tao,

18:32.923 --> 18:34.483
who secured the bank loan

18:34.923 --> 18:35.802
for Yan Studio,

18:35.802 --> 18:36.963
solving our urgent needs.

18:37.203 --> 18:37.683
Thank you.

18:39.203 --> 18:40.842
I just did my job.

18:41.122 --> 18:42.923
It's all due to Ms. Qiao's leadership.

18:45.243 --> 18:46.163
Thank you, Ms. Qiao.

18:46.723 --> 18:47.203
Alright.

18:47.842 --> 18:48.243
Okay.

18:48.362 --> 18:49.163
Let's begin then.

18:49.163 --> 18:50.483
Tell me

18:50.643 --> 18:51.923
the recent project progress.

18:52.643 --> 18:53.082
Yao,

18:53.122 --> 18:54.522
about the batik project,

18:54.522 --> 18:55.163
now...

18:55.443 --> 18:56.282
I've prepared

18:56.282 --> 18:57.802
a plan for the batik collection.

18:57.883 --> 18:58.403
Take a look.

18:59.522 --> 19:00.762
For the new products,

19:00.802 --> 19:02.082
we'll collaborate with

19:02.082 --> 19:04.203
top ten fashion influencers

19:04.203 --> 19:05.403
for videos.

19:05.443 --> 19:06.443
It's almost done.

19:11.003 --> 19:12.322
So he falsified

19:12.322 --> 19:14.384
Yan Studio's

19:14.384 --> 19:15.084
financial reports

19:15.842 --> 19:17.003
and applied for the loan.

19:17.243 --> 19:18.723
All to force you

19:19.562 --> 19:21.443
to return and marry him?

19:23.683 --> 19:24.362
That's why

19:24.362 --> 19:26.003
you moved out, right?

19:28.443 --> 19:30.643
I wanted to keep him calm.

19:31.322 --> 19:33.322
That meant keeping distance

19:33.522 --> 19:35.042
from Yu Yiming temporarily.

19:39.203 --> 19:40.683
Earlier,

19:41.322 --> 19:42.403
he acted diligent

19:42.883 --> 19:44.003
and reliable,

19:44.003 --> 19:45.003
but it was all an act.

19:45.082 --> 19:46.322
He planned all this

19:46.322 --> 19:47.522
long ago, right?

19:51.282 --> 19:52.163
Recently,

19:52.163 --> 19:53.403
I've been thinking

19:53.522 --> 19:55.042
how to handle this.

19:56.723 --> 19:57.762
I've recorded evidence.

20:00.082 --> 20:01.163
I confronted him

20:01.163 --> 20:03.443
and recorded this.

20:03.443 --> 20:04.003
Hear it out.

20:04.762 --> 20:06.163
When did I falsify the accounts?

20:06.802 --> 20:08.203
If you're accusing me of that,

20:08.723 --> 20:09.883
you stamped the seal!

20:10.203 --> 20:10.683
Yes,

20:11.602 --> 20:12.322
I admit

20:12.762 --> 20:14.562
threatening you with loan fraud

20:14.683 --> 20:15.923
was despicable,

20:16.802 --> 20:18.243
but my love for you

20:18.243 --> 20:19.522
is genuine.

20:20.483 --> 20:22.483
I never meant to harm anyone.

20:23.762 --> 20:25.602
I just want you to come back with me.

20:29.562 --> 20:30.842
With this recording,

20:31.122 --> 20:32.923
we can at least prove to the bank

20:32.923 --> 20:34.443
that we aren't part of his scheme.

20:34.802 --> 20:35.683
And we didn't know

20:35.683 --> 20:36.683
about the loan fraud,

20:36.802 --> 20:38.042
nor involved in it.

20:39.883 --> 20:42.362
We've used part of the loan,

20:42.963 --> 20:44.362
but fortunately not much.

20:45.883 --> 20:47.403
I told parents

20:47.683 --> 20:49.082
we're facing

20:49.082 --> 20:50.203
the cash flow problem.

20:50.923 --> 20:51.723
Then they gave us

20:51.923 --> 20:53.122
the pension money

20:53.122 --> 20:54.362
you gave them.

20:55.243 --> 20:56.723
Now the money is ready.

20:56.723 --> 20:58.163
We can repay the bank anytime.

21:01.923 --> 21:02.883
I'm sorry, Yan.

21:03.082 --> 21:04.443
You entrusted me with the company,

21:04.522 --> 21:05.883
and I caused this mess.

21:06.762 --> 21:08.243
This isn't your fault.

21:09.163 --> 21:09.842
Besides,

21:10.042 --> 21:11.003
you got the evidence.

21:11.163 --> 21:12.362
You've done great enough.

21:14.883 --> 21:15.443
By the way,

21:15.923 --> 21:17.403
you mentioned

21:17.723 --> 21:18.923
that Lin Tao raised

21:18.963 --> 21:20.243
the profit margin to 21 percent,

21:20.322 --> 21:21.403
to let us get the loan?

21:21.963 --> 21:22.403
Yes.

21:22.963 --> 21:24.643
Given our high-cost

21:24.683 --> 21:25.762
handmade fabrics,

21:26.203 --> 21:27.522
and the enormous expenses

21:27.522 --> 21:28.483
for promotion,

21:29.403 --> 21:30.282
our company

21:30.282 --> 21:31.483
is in a phase

21:31.643 --> 21:33.883
of seeking the break-even point.

21:36.562 --> 21:37.762
It's impossible to achieve

21:37.762 --> 21:39.082
a 21 percent profit margin.

21:40.802 --> 21:42.443
How could the bank miss this?

21:43.683 --> 21:45.403
The loan officer Feng

21:45.403 --> 21:46.723
is Lin Tao's close friend.

21:46.723 --> 21:47.082
Also...

21:47.082 --> 21:48.082
That is not plausible.

21:48.963 --> 21:50.762
Loan fraud is illegal
and leads to jail time.

21:53.042 --> 21:54.003
Would this Feng

21:54.082 --> 21:55.163
really take

21:55.443 --> 21:56.883
such huge risks

21:57.362 --> 21:58.723
just to help Lin Tao?

22:01.522 --> 22:02.842
Even if there were oversights

22:02.842 --> 22:03.723
in the review process,

22:04.243 --> 22:06.483
both staff and supervisors

22:06.562 --> 22:08.122
would face severe legal liabilities.

22:08.282 --> 22:09.082
In this regard,

22:09.683 --> 22:11.282
banks would be extremely cautious.

22:13.802 --> 22:15.282
This is suspicious.

22:16.403 --> 22:17.562
In that case,

22:19.203 --> 22:20.923
there is something off.

22:21.362 --> 22:21.883
(Manager's Office)
Ms. Qiao,

22:22.322 --> 22:22.923
Lin Tao

22:22.923 --> 22:24.403
has handled the documents.

22:24.522 --> 22:26.762
Just stamp here.

22:27.082 --> 22:27.683
Feng,

22:28.003 --> 22:30.243
thank you for the loan.

22:31.003 --> 22:31.802
(Loan Contract)
Don't worry.

22:31.883 --> 22:32.723
Tao and I

22:32.723 --> 22:33.602
are old friends.

22:33.963 --> 22:35.322
We'll proceed

22:35.562 --> 22:36.443
at the fastest pace.

22:36.683 --> 22:37.723
Thank you.

22:38.082 --> 22:39.122
Truly a lifesaver.

22:39.203 --> 22:40.003
(Party B: Jingzhou Yan Studio Fashion Design Co., Ltd.)
It's nothing.

22:40.122 --> 22:41.082
This should be okay.

22:41.483 --> 22:42.643
Once the funds are released,

22:42.963 --> 22:43.963
I'll notify you.

22:44.163 --> 22:44.802
Feng,

22:44.842 --> 22:46.362
when do you finish work today?

22:46.923 --> 22:48.562
Let's have dinner together tonight.

22:49.322 --> 22:49.602
I...

22:49.602 --> 22:50.042
Ms. Qiao.

22:50.683 --> 22:52.082
I've booked our return tickets.

22:52.163 --> 22:53.483
We need to leave tonight.

22:53.643 --> 22:55.003
Next time then.

22:55.362 --> 22:56.723
Now that we've connected,

22:56.842 --> 22:58.082
there'll be many opportunities.

23:00.963 --> 23:02.082
Next time then.

23:04.122 --> 23:04.723
So Lin Tao

23:04.723 --> 23:06.122
didn't want you

23:06.643 --> 23:07.602
to contact

23:07.602 --> 23:08.923
that Feng.

23:10.723 --> 23:11.282
Now,

23:11.562 --> 23:12.243
the top priority

23:12.643 --> 23:13.963
is to find Feng

23:14.203 --> 23:15.322
and figure out

23:15.562 --> 23:16.802
what's happening

23:16.802 --> 23:17.562
with this loan.

23:18.602 --> 23:19.163
Besides,

23:19.683 --> 23:20.762
I know you don't want

23:21.403 --> 23:22.683
Yu Yiming involved,

23:23.923 --> 23:25.003
but this matter

23:25.562 --> 23:26.762
has nothing to do

23:26.883 --> 23:28.042
with your relationship.

23:29.648 --> 23:30.832
I think

23:30.832 --> 23:32.163
you should be honest with him.

23:35.842 --> 23:36.683
Anyway,

23:37.122 --> 23:39.042
that's how it is.

23:43.403 --> 23:44.562
I know...

23:45.082 --> 23:46.602
I know you'd be upset.

23:57.042 --> 23:58.403
You didn't tell me

23:59.362 --> 24:00.522
because you feared Lin Tao

24:00.522 --> 24:02.092
would escalate things and implicate me.

24:03.762 --> 24:05.282
You've been bearing

24:06.362 --> 24:07.602
all this alone recently.

24:10.723 --> 24:11.602
But from now on,

24:12.403 --> 24:13.842
no matter what happens,

24:14.082 --> 24:15.923
whether it's big or small,

24:16.723 --> 24:18.042
you have to tell me.

24:24.842 --> 24:26.643
I plan to visit my hometown

24:26.923 --> 24:27.802
to find Feng

24:27.842 --> 24:29.923
and see if I can figure out this.

24:30.403 --> 24:30.842
Alright.

24:31.082 --> 24:31.842
I'll go with you.

24:32.042 --> 24:33.322
No need. I can go by myself.

24:33.362 --> 24:33.923
No way.

24:34.883 --> 24:36.042
What if Feng is colluding

24:36.042 --> 24:36.842
with Lin Tao?

24:37.883 --> 24:39.322
What if something happens?

24:40.683 --> 24:42.203
I must go with you.

24:44.042 --> 24:44.602
Alright.

24:49.850 --> 24:51.522
(Yan Studio)

24:51.522 --> 24:52.522
Currently,

24:52.602 --> 24:54.203
apart from our production line's

24:54.203 --> 24:55.282
steady output,

24:55.643 --> 24:56.282
I want you all

24:56.282 --> 24:57.723
to focus on

24:57.723 --> 24:58.483
pushing forward

24:58.483 --> 24:59.963
with the physical store expansion.

25:00.282 --> 25:01.562
Four key points to note.

25:02.003 --> 25:02.562
First,

25:02.802 --> 25:04.243
window display designs.

25:04.683 --> 25:05.082
Second,

25:05.163 --> 25:06.562
pre-launch marketing campaigns.

25:07.003 --> 25:07.602
Third,

25:07.923 --> 25:09.082
staff service training.

25:09.122 --> 25:09.683
Fourth,

25:10.082 --> 25:11.163
supply chain reliability.

25:11.522 --> 25:12.362
All departments must

25:12.362 --> 25:13.282
offer timely feedback.

25:13.483 --> 25:14.643
Besides,

25:15.322 --> 25:16.322
there will be

25:16.322 --> 25:17.562
more staff.

25:17.723 --> 25:18.762
If you need anything,

25:18.762 --> 25:20.282
inform HR.

25:23.042 --> 25:23.562
Qiao Lin,

25:24.443 --> 25:25.163
a mall in Tianjin

25:25.163 --> 25:26.122
invites us to set up

25:26.122 --> 25:28.082
a physical store there.

25:29.003 --> 25:29.562
This is

25:29.562 --> 25:30.443
a good opportunity.

25:30.842 --> 25:32.003
You'll go discuss

25:32.003 --> 25:33.042
the details thoroughly.

25:33.362 --> 25:33.762
Okay.

25:34.322 --> 25:35.082
Mr. Lin.

25:35.602 --> 25:37.042
We're pushing forward

25:37.042 --> 25:38.643
with the physical store project,

25:38.683 --> 25:39.842
so the financial work

25:39.842 --> 25:40.522
will increase.

25:40.522 --> 25:41.243
Please handle it.

25:41.762 --> 25:42.923
I'm glad

25:42.963 --> 25:44.362
that the company is thriving.

25:46.802 --> 25:47.522
Please compile

25:47.522 --> 25:49.003
the budgets of all departments

25:49.003 --> 25:50.403
and put them in my office.

25:50.562 --> 25:51.082
I want

25:51.082 --> 25:52.322
our petty cash reserve

25:52.322 --> 25:53.443
adjusted to three percent.

25:53.522 --> 25:54.203
No problem.

25:56.723 --> 25:57.723
On Wednesday,

25:58.602 --> 25:59.643
I'll discuss it with you.

26:00.443 --> 26:00.883
Okay.

26:03.082 --> 26:03.562
Okay.

26:03.723 --> 26:04.802
Please state

26:04.802 --> 26:06.042
your budgets.

26:06.483 --> 26:07.403
Lin Tao, take notes.

26:08.643 --> 26:09.163
Huanhuan,

26:09.282 --> 26:10.322
what's the biggest expense

26:10.403 --> 26:11.963
in promotion?

26:12.122 --> 26:12.923
It's mainly about

26:12.923 --> 26:14.282
KOL collaborations

26:14.282 --> 26:15.762
and organizing offline events.

26:16.042 --> 26:17.483
We plan to launch

26:17.483 --> 26:19.243
a physical store check-in campaign,

26:19.602 --> 26:21.042
posting featuring Yan Studio...

26:26.170 --> 26:27.122
(Yan Studio)

26:27.122 --> 26:27.723
What's wrong?

26:27.802 --> 26:28.602
What's the matter?

26:34.322 --> 26:35.602
When will you return?

26:37.403 --> 26:38.683
I'll go early tomorrow

26:38.762 --> 26:40.082
and have a dinner.

26:40.176 --> 26:40.842
I will be back

26:40.842 --> 26:42.042
by the morning after next.

26:42.802 --> 26:43.443
Don't worry.

26:43.443 --> 26:44.963
It won't delay our trip back home.

26:47.683 --> 26:49.403
Now that the company is back on track,

26:50.122 --> 26:51.362
and everything goes smoothly,

26:51.643 --> 26:52.883
I must keep

26:53.122 --> 26:54.923
my promise.

26:58.923 --> 26:59.562
I know.

27:00.802 --> 27:02.163
I'm not pushing you.

27:06.203 --> 27:07.042
Enough talk.

27:08.042 --> 27:09.483
Time will prove everything.

27:31.403 --> 27:31.963
(Qiao Lin.)

27:32.282 --> 27:33.562
(Remember this place?)

27:34.122 --> 27:35.883
Where you asked me to dinner last time.

27:37.802 --> 27:39.403
I've prepared something special.

27:40.842 --> 27:41.762
Balloons,

27:43.082 --> 27:43.963
flowers,

27:44.643 --> 27:45.403
and champagne.

27:47.522 --> 27:48.282
Most importantly,

27:50.042 --> 27:51.042
there's us two.

27:54.082 --> 27:55.122
Will you marry me?

27:56.163 --> 27:57.163
Yu Yiming?

27:59.602 --> 28:00.243
Lin.

28:00.883 --> 28:01.643
What's going on?

28:02.403 --> 28:03.683
Why do you bring him here?

28:07.522 --> 28:08.042
Lin.

28:08.163 --> 28:09.483
Look, I've bought the ring.

28:09.883 --> 28:11.483
Let's go back at 11 AM

28:11.762 --> 28:12.683
this Saturday

28:13.042 --> 28:13.322
to...

28:13.322 --> 28:14.643
Lin won't go back with you,

28:15.842 --> 28:16.963
nor will she marry you.

28:26.602 --> 28:27.443
Broke your promise?

28:27.923 --> 28:29.562
I've helped you.

28:30.842 --> 28:32.322
Now you're backing out?

28:35.203 --> 28:36.762
Didn't I make myself clear?

28:37.963 --> 28:40.082
You should know the consequences.

28:42.443 --> 28:43.963
We know about the loan.

28:47.362 --> 28:48.883
You went to see Feng?

28:49.483 --> 28:50.562
You assumed

28:50.842 --> 28:51.762
that I would

28:51.762 --> 28:52.643
fear escalation.

28:53.723 --> 28:54.522
You also assumed

28:54.522 --> 28:56.122
that I wouldn't dare approach the bank.

28:57.163 --> 28:58.842
You thought

28:59.163 --> 29:00.122
we would

29:00.122 --> 29:01.243
accept this loan,

29:01.483 --> 29:02.522
make regular payments,

29:03.163 --> 29:05.003
and never mention it again.

29:05.322 --> 29:06.802
But how is that possible?

29:07.322 --> 29:08.723
If this were loan fraud,

29:09.042 --> 29:10.322
I'd face legal consequences

29:10.602 --> 29:12.522
because I stamped the seal

29:13.042 --> 29:14.003
and it's my negligence.

29:14.362 --> 29:15.683
That's what I planned to do.

29:16.762 --> 29:18.082
When I met with Feng,

29:18.362 --> 29:19.723
I wanted to explain the situation,

29:19.723 --> 29:20.683
but then I discovered

29:21.282 --> 29:22.122
you never

29:22.122 --> 29:23.163
falsified the accounts.

29:23.562 --> 29:24.163
You gave him

29:24.163 --> 29:25.643
the authentic financial records,

29:25.723 --> 29:27.082
so he approved the loan.

29:27.362 --> 29:28.163
So, you didn't

29:28.163 --> 29:29.203
want me to dine with him.

29:29.643 --> 29:30.602
You lied to me,

29:30.842 --> 29:32.003
gave me fake reports,

29:32.122 --> 29:33.042
and made me stamp them,

29:33.562 --> 29:34.643
in order to get me back

29:34.643 --> 29:36.042
and marry you.

29:37.602 --> 29:38.322
Lin Tao.

29:38.802 --> 29:39.883
You had a conscience

29:40.082 --> 29:41.243
and didn't commit loan fraud.

29:42.122 --> 29:42.643
Otherwise,

29:42.643 --> 29:43.883
we'd be at the police station.

29:45.082 --> 29:46.122
I could sue you,

29:47.443 --> 29:49.042
but I want to show some mercy.

29:49.643 --> 29:53.443
So, please leave.

29:55.683 --> 29:56.403
Lin Tao.

29:57.082 --> 29:58.322
Stop all these schemes.

29:58.602 --> 29:59.883
Especially leave Qiao Lin alone.

30:01.443 --> 30:02.602
Or I won't let you off.

30:18.282 --> 30:20.403
Sir, should we serve the dishes?

30:20.883 --> 30:22.163
Get out!

30:30.483 --> 30:31.282
What?

30:43.602 --> 30:45.163
I've received the email.

30:45.762 --> 30:46.963
You want me

30:47.322 --> 30:49.723
to sign a performance-based agreement,

30:50.003 --> 30:50.522
right?

30:50.643 --> 30:51.243
Mr. Qu.

30:51.483 --> 30:52.643
As the head

30:52.723 --> 30:53.762
of the group,

30:54.322 --> 30:55.003
you've planned

30:55.003 --> 30:56.443
to bid for the North Waichuan plot,

30:56.883 --> 30:57.683
and proposed

30:57.802 --> 30:58.683
if the bid succeeds,

30:58.683 --> 30:59.643
we'll terminate early

30:59.643 --> 31:01.203
your one-year probation period.

31:01.203 --> 31:01.762
Right?

31:04.163 --> 31:05.403
This bid could transform

31:05.403 --> 31:07.082
the real estate landscape.

31:08.163 --> 31:10.362
The demands seem reasonable, right?

31:12.963 --> 31:14.042
But if you fail,

31:14.403 --> 31:16.322
Jinda's stock will plummet.

31:16.443 --> 31:17.883
You're newly appointed.

31:18.003 --> 31:18.762
The shareholders

31:18.963 --> 31:20.362
have reservations.

31:20.602 --> 31:21.443
Hence, they proposed

31:21.443 --> 31:23.243
a performance-based agreement.

31:24.003 --> 31:24.643
If you succeed,

31:24.683 --> 31:26.082
your probation will end early.

31:26.203 --> 31:27.042
If you fail,

31:27.362 --> 31:28.602
the Chairman position

31:28.683 --> 31:30.203
will be up for re-election.

31:31.163 --> 31:31.643
Mr. Qu.

31:32.483 --> 31:33.282
Don't get us wrong.

31:33.963 --> 31:35.362
This isn't personal.

31:35.963 --> 31:37.122
Every new chairman

31:37.122 --> 31:37.883
must undergo

31:38.203 --> 31:39.643
such challenges in their probation.

31:39.842 --> 31:40.362
After all,

31:40.483 --> 31:42.082
the shareholders want to see

31:42.243 --> 31:43.522
solid financial performance.

31:44.122 --> 31:45.163
That applies to everyone.

31:51.522 --> 31:52.723
I'm back.

31:54.322 --> 31:55.203
How's Haochen doing?

31:55.723 --> 31:57.483
He's been doing great.

31:57.883 --> 31:59.082
I met Miss Sun

31:59.082 --> 31:59.883
and greeted her.

32:00.122 --> 32:00.802
If there's

32:00.802 --> 32:01.883
any problem with Haochen,

32:01.883 --> 32:03.082
she'll contact us.

32:05.602 --> 32:07.522
Anyway, don't worry.

32:08.443 --> 32:08.963
Everything

32:08.963 --> 32:10.243
is getting better.

32:12.082 --> 32:12.762
Haochen

32:12.762 --> 32:14.003
asked to go back to school.

32:14.082 --> 32:15.163
That's truly remarkable.

32:15.883 --> 32:16.723
My mom is also

32:17.003 --> 32:18.203
grateful to you and Grandma.

32:19.723 --> 32:21.003
If she puts it that way,

32:21.362 --> 32:22.562
it feels too formal.

32:24.003 --> 32:24.842
Haochen gets better,

32:24.963 --> 32:26.243
and our family will be better.

32:28.802 --> 32:29.362
Alright.

32:33.403 --> 32:35.522
How's your physical store project?

32:36.082 --> 32:37.122
Everything is on track.

32:37.602 --> 32:39.443
The renovation
is more than halfway done.

32:39.842 --> 32:41.403
And Yao has completed

32:41.403 --> 32:42.842
the botanical dyeing series designs.

32:42.842 --> 32:44.082
I'll see them today.

32:44.683 --> 32:45.282
Great.

32:47.362 --> 32:48.762
What's your plan?

32:51.203 --> 32:53.723
Bid for the North Waichuan plot.

32:54.602 --> 32:56.683
Qu Mingcheng made other shareholders

32:56.802 --> 32:58.003
sue me and my dad,

32:58.883 --> 33:01.522
demanding us
to compensate the group's losses.

33:02.082 --> 33:03.762
Our accounts are frozen,

33:04.362 --> 33:06.163
and we lost our positions at Jinda.

33:06.602 --> 33:07.762
Everyone thinks

33:07.842 --> 33:09.883
I couldn't win the bid

33:10.403 --> 33:11.522
for this Diamond Plot.

33:13.203 --> 33:14.963
I know I can't win forever,

33:15.762 --> 33:17.203
but for Dad and Haochen,

33:17.963 --> 33:19.403
I won't lose to Qu Mingcheng.

33:24.923 --> 33:26.683
Which company will you use for the bid?

33:27.082 --> 33:28.203
My dad's first company,

33:28.883 --> 33:29.683
called Xinye.

33:30.443 --> 33:32.163
Our core team members

33:32.443 --> 33:33.483
have all resigned

33:34.282 --> 33:35.483
and will stick with me.

33:37.203 --> 33:39.082
I have the confidence and energy

33:39.282 --> 33:40.322
to continue bidding.

33:40.842 --> 33:42.842
And thank you for your help too.

33:46.602 --> 33:48.042
I don't accept verbal thanks.

33:49.203 --> 33:50.602
If you want to thank me,

33:52.322 --> 33:53.362
do it properly

33:53.683 --> 33:54.562
when you succeed.

33:55.522 --> 33:56.042
Yes.

33:57.322 --> 33:57.883
By the way,

33:58.883 --> 34:00.203
you're meeting Mr. Huang, right?

34:00.403 --> 34:00.762
Yes.

34:01.643 --> 34:02.602
Your suit and tie

34:02.602 --> 34:03.723
are upstairs.

34:05.723 --> 34:06.322
See?

34:06.443 --> 34:08.522
Thank you very much for your support.

34:08.602 --> 34:09.403
I told you

34:09.403 --> 34:11.042
I don't accept verbal thanks.

34:14.202 --> 34:14.722
Haoming.

34:15.283 --> 34:17.202
Is everything going smoothly
in the new company?

34:17.763 --> 34:18.283
Pretty well.

34:18.923 --> 34:19.883
I hope

34:20.122 --> 34:21.843
I can collaborate with you.

34:23.082 --> 34:24.082
To be honest,

34:24.443 --> 34:26.682
without capital

34:26.722 --> 34:27.763
or corporate backing,

34:28.443 --> 34:29.883
how can I cooperate with you?

34:31.562 --> 34:32.602
Four years ago,

34:33.642 --> 34:34.682
when North Waichuan's

34:35.363 --> 34:36.883
development plans were announced,

34:38.122 --> 34:39.202
my team and I

34:39.202 --> 34:40.003
started monitoring.

34:40.642 --> 34:41.483
About land supply,

34:41.883 --> 34:42.923
policy directions,

34:43.162 --> 34:44.363
municipal planning,

34:44.682 --> 34:46.963
and our competitors' strategies,

34:47.363 --> 34:48.562
we've conducted the research.

34:48.963 --> 34:50.162
I'll offer the proposal.

34:50.443 --> 34:51.443
You'll offer the capital.

34:52.483 --> 34:53.522
Let's bid jointly.

34:57.722 --> 34:58.722
For this project,

34:59.283 --> 35:01.642
I'm not pursuing profits,

35:03.443 --> 35:05.122
but to defeat Qu Mingcheng.

35:35.682 --> 35:36.162
Mr. Huang.

35:36.202 --> 35:36.883
Mr. Qu is here.

35:37.403 --> 35:37.963
Let him in.

35:38.363 --> 35:38.923
Mr. Qu.

35:39.562 --> 35:40.403
There's no denying

35:40.483 --> 35:42.363
your offer is very generous,

35:44.042 --> 35:45.283
but I have reservations.

35:45.843 --> 35:47.283
Shen Haoming is young.

35:47.323 --> 35:48.443
You can say

35:48.443 --> 35:50.242
he doesn't hold much sway
in the group yet.

35:50.763 --> 35:51.923
But Shen Jinsong

35:52.122 --> 35:54.283
is the founder of Jinda Group.

35:54.443 --> 35:56.242
He's managed the group for decades.

35:56.562 --> 35:58.162
The shareholders

35:58.242 --> 36:00.122
may seem to be on your side now.

36:01.082 --> 36:02.682
But once Shen Jinsong recovers

36:02.682 --> 36:03.722
and returns to the group,

36:04.122 --> 36:06.722
where will their loyalties lie?

36:08.843 --> 36:09.722
Shen Jinsong

36:09.763 --> 36:11.403
can't even take care of himself now.

36:11.602 --> 36:12.602
He's completely

36:12.602 --> 36:13.722
out of this battlefield.

36:14.283 --> 36:15.122
Nothing to fear.

36:18.562 --> 36:19.923
Bring me the documents

36:19.923 --> 36:21.162
about the bank credit loans.

36:21.722 --> 36:22.242
Here.

36:22.522 --> 36:23.042
Here.

36:24.202 --> 36:25.162
This endorsement...

36:25.483 --> 36:25.883
Okay.

36:26.242 --> 36:27.323
Compile the data.

36:27.763 --> 36:29.162
No. 9.

36:29.264 --> 36:29.744
(Project Objectives and Significance)

36:30.602 --> 36:31.242
Note this down.

36:32.403 --> 36:33.323
Good news!

36:34.202 --> 36:34.763
Mr. Chen

36:34.843 --> 36:36.082
will invest in our project.

36:36.722 --> 36:37.162
Really?

36:37.763 --> 36:38.323
Fantastic!

36:44.003 --> 36:44.602
How's this?

36:45.042 --> 36:45.763
Can you keep up?

36:46.843 --> 36:47.483
Mr. Huang.

36:48.042 --> 36:49.483
You run marathons every year,

36:50.042 --> 36:50.963
even full distances.

36:51.562 --> 36:52.642
I need more practice.

36:52.923 --> 36:53.602
Haoming,

36:54.003 --> 36:54.722
I enjoy

36:54.722 --> 36:56.042
teaming up with young people.

36:56.283 --> 36:57.283
You're energetic

36:57.323 --> 36:58.003
and resilient.

36:59.082 --> 37:00.003
I run alone

37:00.003 --> 37:01.242
by this lake every day,

37:01.283 --> 37:03.042
with no one to share

37:03.242 --> 37:04.162
such beautiful scenery.

37:05.403 --> 37:05.923
By the way,

37:06.363 --> 37:07.443
the proposal is ready.

37:08.082 --> 37:09.242
We can submit it soon.

37:10.122 --> 37:10.722
Haoming.

37:11.602 --> 37:12.522
I know

37:13.042 --> 37:14.122
your vision, energy,

37:14.242 --> 37:15.323
and strategic mindset.

37:17.122 --> 37:18.202
I'm getting old.

37:18.562 --> 37:19.403
I am not

37:19.602 --> 37:20.883
what I used to be.

37:21.242 --> 37:22.562
I've wanted to retire.

37:23.042 --> 37:24.883
Make some investments and enjoy life.

37:25.642 --> 37:27.483
But working with you

37:28.562 --> 37:29.323
makes me feel

37:29.323 --> 37:30.602
rejuvenated.

37:30.963 --> 37:31.602
I think

37:31.763 --> 37:32.923
I could still work.

37:33.522 --> 37:34.042
Mr. Huang.

37:34.522 --> 37:35.722
Don't retire yet.

37:35.923 --> 37:38.522
Stay and let us learn from you.

37:39.403 --> 37:39.843
Let's go.

37:40.283 --> 37:40.763
Haoming.

37:43.283 --> 37:44.042
Sorry.

37:45.883 --> 37:46.883
But for the second half,

37:47.443 --> 37:48.443
I want to run alone.

38:27.042 --> 38:28.443
That cunning Huang Chuming.

38:28.883 --> 38:29.883
We made the proposal

38:29.883 --> 38:31.202
as a joint venture until now.

38:31.642 --> 38:32.883
The funding section especially

38:33.403 --> 38:33.963
was crucial

38:33.963 --> 38:35.202
for winning the bid.

38:35.883 --> 38:36.562
But he

38:37.122 --> 38:38.323
pulls out his investment

38:38.323 --> 38:39.323
without warning.

38:40.443 --> 38:42.202
Revise our bidding strategy now

38:42.363 --> 38:43.082
is impossible.

38:44.803 --> 38:46.283
With Mr. Huang's investment,

38:46.682 --> 38:47.363
we would

38:47.363 --> 38:48.562
at least have a support

38:49.082 --> 38:50.192
and stand a chance

38:50.192 --> 38:51.088
against Qu Mingcheng.

38:51.403 --> 38:53.003
But he withdraws

38:53.042 --> 38:53.843
his investment,

38:54.122 --> 38:56.082
we stand no chance now.

38:56.722 --> 38:57.443
In my opinion,

38:57.722 --> 38:59.003
better to cut losses early

38:59.202 --> 39:00.202
than crash and burn.

39:00.403 --> 39:01.082
I suggest

39:01.642 --> 39:02.963
we withdraw from this bid.

39:03.283 --> 39:04.483
Why gamble

39:04.682 --> 39:06.283
on such a risky bid?

39:08.363 --> 39:08.923
Mr. Shen.

39:09.162 --> 39:10.003
What do you think?

39:12.042 --> 39:12.923
Continue.

39:16.602 --> 39:17.162
We've been

39:17.202 --> 39:18.522
prepping for ages.

39:19.923 --> 39:21.522
I don't want to waste your hard work.

39:22.242 --> 39:24.843
Let's revise the proposal

39:25.162 --> 39:26.003
and submit it.

39:26.403 --> 39:27.682
Do it with

39:27.722 --> 39:29.682
the minimum 1 percent deposit.

39:31.003 --> 39:31.763
Why?

39:32.562 --> 39:34.122
Even if we fail, so what?

39:34.803 --> 39:35.443
Consider this

39:35.443 --> 39:37.162
our debut in the industry.

39:37.722 --> 39:38.763
Winning doesn't matter.

39:39.323 --> 39:40.483
I don't want others

39:40.722 --> 39:42.082
to think losing one partner

39:42.162 --> 39:43.403
makes us stuck

39:44.042 --> 39:44.722
and even lose

39:44.722 --> 39:45.722
the courage

39:45.722 --> 39:46.363
to compete.

39:47.963 --> 39:48.682
Keep discussing

39:48.883 --> 39:49.682
the proposal.

39:53.202 --> 39:54.003
Check if our project

39:54.042 --> 39:54.642
has green space

39:54.763 --> 39:55.803
development plans.

40:04.082 --> 40:05.162
Still working?

40:08.003 --> 40:09.003
It's late now.

40:11.042 --> 40:13.122
We might fail

40:13.202 --> 40:14.443
this Diamond Plot bidding,

40:14.843 --> 40:16.483
but as a new company,

40:16.883 --> 40:18.403
having a viable project

40:19.122 --> 40:20.602
builds market reputation.

40:25.642 --> 40:26.682
Found any suitable one?

40:26.843 --> 40:27.323
Yes.

40:27.803 --> 40:28.443
Take a look

40:28.963 --> 40:29.522
at this.

40:36.464 --> 40:36.923
(Shikumen Renovation Project)

40:36.923 --> 40:37.883
Shikumen?

40:38.843 --> 40:39.443
It is

40:39.443 --> 40:40.562
a renovation project.

40:41.522 --> 40:42.522
Pretty nice.

40:46.642 --> 40:47.722
The collaboration

40:47.722 --> 40:49.242
with Gubei Town

40:49.323 --> 40:50.283
makes me realize

40:50.283 --> 40:51.082
the governments'

40:51.443 --> 40:54.642
efforts on cultural preservation.

40:55.283 --> 40:56.202
It has reached

40:56.202 --> 40:57.443
new heights recently.

41:00.602 --> 41:01.803
So this direction is correct.

41:02.522 --> 41:03.202
Exactly.

41:07.003 --> 41:07.483
What?

41:10.202 --> 41:11.042
Your hair.

41:13.562 --> 41:14.283
Wrap it up

41:14.522 --> 41:15.403
and get some rest.

41:15.602 --> 41:16.082
Okay.

41:19.082 --> 41:19.883
Need company?

41:20.923 --> 41:21.803
No need.

41:21.963 --> 41:22.883
I'll be up shortly.

41:23.283 --> 41:23.803
Alright.

42:01.162 --> 42:01.803
Any progress?

42:02.042 --> 42:03.562
Yes.

42:04.162 --> 42:04.923
Good then.

42:05.722 --> 42:06.323
Go to sleep.

42:15.042 --> 42:16.122
I heard Shen Haoming

42:16.122 --> 42:17.522
landed a government-backed

42:17.843 --> 42:18.722
renovation project.

42:19.722 --> 42:20.562
Exactly.

42:21.162 --> 42:22.363
The cooperation is confirmed.

42:23.722 --> 42:24.682
He is

42:25.162 --> 42:26.483
quite smart,

42:27.202 --> 42:28.242
taking some projects

42:28.522 --> 42:29.642
to sustain his startup.

42:32.323 --> 42:34.042
Where's Weiping?

42:36.283 --> 42:37.803
You set up a new firm for him.

42:38.162 --> 42:39.242
As a rookie entrepreneur,

42:39.443 --> 42:40.122
he's swamped.

42:45.162 --> 42:46.003
Anything else?

42:48.323 --> 42:48.883
Mr. Qu.

42:49.483 --> 42:50.042
I know

42:50.042 --> 42:51.162
you promised Weiping

42:51.803 --> 42:53.963
to let Jinda's legal team

42:54.682 --> 42:55.483
channel our projects

42:55.483 --> 42:56.522
to his firm.

42:58.042 --> 42:58.763
However,

42:59.602 --> 43:00.602
I've reviewed

43:00.602 --> 43:01.682
another firm's proposal

43:03.923 --> 43:05.042
that outperforms

43:05.122 --> 43:06.283
his firm

43:06.283 --> 43:06.883
in every way.

43:09.803 --> 43:11.803
But I promised Weiping.

43:11.883 --> 43:12.403
Mr. Qu.

43:13.162 --> 43:14.443
Appointing me to the board

43:14.642 --> 43:15.403
has displeased

43:15.403 --> 43:16.562
those shareholders.

43:17.602 --> 43:19.242
If we channel our projects

43:19.363 --> 43:21.122
to a new firm,

43:22.042 --> 43:23.963
they might suspect

43:24.443 --> 43:25.803
your relationship with Weiping.

43:29.483 --> 43:30.682
How about this?

43:31.042 --> 43:32.363
Let's have a transitional period.

43:32.883 --> 43:33.682
Anyway,

43:33.682 --> 43:34.522
we can channel

43:35.082 --> 43:36.843
the projects to Weiping later.

43:43.642 --> 43:45.122
Then explain this properly to him.

43:45.883 --> 43:47.483
Avoid causing unnecessary trouble.

43:48.283 --> 43:48.963
Rest assured.

44:00.407 --> 44:01.584
(Han Weiping)

44:09.443 --> 44:10.042
Hello.

44:10.323 --> 44:11.562
Meet me at the downstairs cafÃ©.

44:12.162 --> 44:12.682
Now.

44:12.682 --> 44:14.416
(Jinda Group)

44:15.122 --> 44:16.843
It's not up to you.

44:17.483 --> 44:18.042
My godfather

44:18.042 --> 44:18.923
has promised me

44:19.483 --> 44:21.042
to sign a long-term agreement

44:21.242 --> 44:22.642
with my firm.

44:23.283 --> 44:24.003
You asked me here

44:24.003 --> 44:25.122
just to discuss this?

44:27.522 --> 44:28.403
Your godfather is busy

44:28.403 --> 44:29.722
with the North Waichuan plot.

44:30.323 --> 44:31.722
This is the top priority now.

44:33.202 --> 44:34.642
Can't you distinguish priorities?

44:35.843 --> 44:36.642
Steve.

44:38.602 --> 44:39.923
You're behind this, right?

44:42.003 --> 44:42.923
I strongly suspect

44:42.923 --> 44:44.562
this agreement will still be mine.

44:50.722 --> 44:51.283
Weiping.

44:52.003 --> 44:52.602
I understand

44:52.602 --> 44:53.602
how you feel right now.

44:55.443 --> 44:56.363
However,

44:57.323 --> 44:58.283
you did engage in

44:58.283 --> 44:59.323
shady activities

45:00.003 --> 45:01.242
for your godfather.

45:02.042 --> 45:02.963
But now,

45:03.363 --> 45:04.722
it's a critical period.

45:05.483 --> 45:07.042
Mr. Qu has to be cautious.

45:07.763 --> 45:08.602
Please understand.

45:12.003 --> 45:14.042
Trying to kick me out now?

45:14.682 --> 45:16.003
To take down the Shen family,

45:16.522 --> 45:18.443
do you know how much I sacrificed?

45:18.642 --> 45:20.122
The incident with Haochen last time

45:20.562 --> 45:21.883
got me detained by police,

45:22.602 --> 45:24.122
and I even lost my lawyer's license.

45:24.803 --> 45:25.963
I've lost everything.

45:27.883 --> 45:28.722
I'm going upstairs

45:28.722 --> 45:29.722
to ask my godfather.

45:32.483 --> 45:34.283
Aren't you afraid

45:34.602 --> 45:35.923
it will cost your other hand too?

45:42.042 --> 45:42.883
Young man,

45:45.042 --> 45:45.923
don't be so impulsive.

45:54.443 --> 45:54.963
Mr. Qu.

45:55.682 --> 45:56.403
Want to see me?

45:57.403 --> 45:57.763
Haoming.

45:57.763 --> 45:58.602
Have a seat.

45:59.403 --> 46:00.082
Have a seat.

46:07.923 --> 46:08.642
Haoming.

46:09.963 --> 46:10.803
Actually,

46:12.003 --> 46:13.562
this adversarial situation between us

46:14.642 --> 46:15.883
isn't what I want.

46:17.682 --> 46:18.642
I don't have children.

46:19.602 --> 46:20.323
Since childhood,

46:20.722 --> 46:21.883
you've been close to me.

46:23.843 --> 46:24.682
To be honest,

46:25.363 --> 46:26.242
sometimes

46:26.443 --> 46:27.843
I genuinely envy your dad

46:27.843 --> 46:29.082
for having a son like you.

46:30.323 --> 46:31.443
My resentment

46:31.763 --> 46:34.162
is solely toward your dad.

46:36.042 --> 46:36.883
Think about it.

46:37.122 --> 46:38.242
If he had shown

46:38.562 --> 46:40.682
more consideration to an old comrade

46:40.763 --> 46:41.923
like me,

46:42.843 --> 46:44.403
then the ones

46:44.483 --> 46:45.283
to celebrate success

46:45.283 --> 46:46.242
would be us.

46:48.602 --> 46:49.682
You asked me to come

46:50.522 --> 46:52.003
not for sentimental talk, right?

46:54.843 --> 46:56.162
Your dad's hospitalization

46:56.722 --> 46:58.283
isn't what I want.

46:58.763 --> 47:00.003
Now you've

47:00.082 --> 47:01.483
started a small company

47:02.283 --> 47:03.283
and are taking on

47:03.283 --> 47:04.283
government projects.

47:04.323 --> 47:05.483
Taking the safe route

47:06.562 --> 47:07.763
seems wise.

47:10.283 --> 47:11.162
If...

47:11.562 --> 47:12.642
I mean, if.

47:13.323 --> 47:15.003
If you want to,

47:16.562 --> 47:17.682
I can

47:18.122 --> 47:20.122
buy your shares

47:20.602 --> 47:21.843
from you and your dad

47:21.883 --> 47:22.963
at a favorable price.

47:23.803 --> 47:25.162
As for the compensation lawsuit,

47:25.763 --> 47:27.003
we can withdraw it.

47:27.522 --> 47:29.803
This is the best for you.

47:34.323 --> 47:35.122
Jinda

47:35.722 --> 47:37.363
was built from scratch by my dad.

47:38.003 --> 47:39.082
We won't sell

47:39.122 --> 47:40.162
any shares.

47:47.522 --> 47:48.562
This is

47:48.722 --> 47:49.602
my best offer

47:49.602 --> 47:50.803
to you two.

47:52.602 --> 47:53.963
If you reject,

47:55.483 --> 47:56.682
you and your dad will have

47:56.722 --> 47:58.003
to go against the entire group.

47:58.562 --> 48:01.363
You'll end up bankrupt.

48:09.530 --> 48:23.024
(North Waichuan Plot 1137
Bidding Conference)

48:52.522 --> 48:53.763
(North Waichuan Plot 1137 Bidding Conference)
Hello,

48:53.883 --> 48:54.883
ladies and gentlemen,

48:55.003 --> 48:55.803
morning.

48:56.283 --> 48:57.162
Welcome to

48:57.162 --> 48:58.843
the North Waichuan Plot 1137

48:58.843 --> 48:59.803
bidding conference.

49:00.363 --> 49:01.483
Today's bidding

49:01.602 --> 49:02.803
will be supervised

49:02.803 --> 49:03.843
by inspection authorities

49:03.883 --> 49:05.283
(North Waichuan Plot 1137 Bidding Conference)
and municipal notary office

49:05.883 --> 49:06.803
to ensure fairness,

49:07.122 --> 49:08.682
justice, and transparency.

49:09.202 --> 49:10.602
This bidding project

49:11.283 --> 49:12.642
involves comprehensive development

49:12.642 --> 49:15.162
of North Waichuan Plot 1137.

49:17.082 --> 49:18.242
All participating companies

49:19.162 --> 49:20.522
must strictly comply with

49:21.042 --> 49:22.562
the People's Republic of China's

49:22.682 --> 49:23.682
Bidding Law

49:23.682 --> 49:26.042
and relevant regulations.

49:26.584 --> 49:27.664
Maintain strict discipline.

49:28.242 --> 49:30.003
Any illegal activities

49:30.963 --> 49:32.082
will be severely punished.

49:33.042 --> 49:33.843
And then

49:34.122 --> 49:35.443
we invite supervisors to examine

49:35.443 --> 49:37.042
the sealed bidding documents.

49:37.042 --> 49:37.562
(North Waichuan Plot 1137
Bidding Conference)

49:37.562 --> 49:38.843
During inspection,

49:39.323 --> 49:41.562
raise objections if any,

49:42.042 --> 49:43.883
otherwise documents
will be deemed sealed.

49:43.883 --> 49:45.392
(Bidding Documents)

49:56.562 --> 49:57.323
All seals intact,

49:57.443 --> 49:58.602
meeting the requirements.

50:02.682 --> 50:03.443
Hold on.

50:05.722 --> 50:07.843
Sorry for interrupting.

50:18.763 --> 50:19.722
These are

50:20.202 --> 50:22.763
(North Waichuan Plot 1137 Bidding Conference)
internal documents

50:23.003 --> 50:25.722
from Jinda, Shijia, Wanlin,

50:25.803 --> 50:27.682
and my employer Shouke.

50:28.483 --> 50:30.363
They detail

50:30.642 --> 50:31.803
bidding strategy

50:32.042 --> 50:34.242
and bidding collusion scheme.

50:35.483 --> 50:37.602
I personally accuse

50:38.323 --> 50:41.003
Jinda Group Chairman Qu Mingcheng

50:42.162 --> 50:43.843
of orchestrating this

50:44.363 --> 50:46.883
bidding collusion operation.

51:02.122 --> 51:03.003
When arriving,

51:03.283 --> 51:04.722
did you see that car downstairs?

51:05.042 --> 51:05.642
I saw it.

51:07.562 --> 51:09.003
My every move now

51:10.082 --> 51:11.522
is being monitored by Qu Mingcheng.

51:12.522 --> 51:14.363
He's afraid you'll make a move.

51:15.003 --> 51:16.363
But he never expected

51:17.443 --> 51:19.003
you would side with me.

51:20.363 --> 51:20.923
Alright.

51:21.522 --> 51:22.363
You can go now.

51:22.602 --> 51:23.682
He'll come up shortly.

51:32.522 --> 51:34.443
Representatives

51:34.522 --> 51:35.722
from Jinda, Shijia and Wanlin

51:35.803 --> 51:37.122
must come with us.

51:38.162 --> 51:38.963
Besides,

51:39.283 --> 51:40.363
Shouke's representative

51:40.522 --> 51:41.562
as a whistleblower,

51:42.003 --> 51:43.082
must assist investigations.

52:02.266 --> 52:05.843
(North Waichuan Plot 1137
Bidding Conference)

52:05.843 --> 52:06.923
Due to accidental reasons,

52:07.803 --> 52:09.923
per investment committee decision,

52:11.122 --> 52:12.722
this conference is suspended.

52:13.122 --> 52:14.963
Resumption will be notified later.

52:15.403 --> 52:16.162
Thank you.

